-- Drill ban could be lifted if Obama conditions met: U.S.
-- 
-- Wed Aug 4, 2010 2:10pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/08/04/us-oil-spill-moratorium-idUSTRE6725ME20100804

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - President Barack Obama would be willing to lift a moratorium on new deepwater oil drilling before November if the conditions he has set are met before then, White House spokesman Robert Gibbs said on Wednesday. 

 (Reporting by  Matt Spetalnick )